<tr id="L315"><td><a href="#L315">315</a></td><td>PICARD:  Being the only Klingon ever to serve in Starfleet gave you a singular distinction, but I felt that what was unique about you was your humanity, compassion, generosity, fairness. You took the best qualities of humanity and made them part of you. The result was a man who I was proud to call one of my officers. I'll have your belongings transported to the Bortas.</td></tr>

<tr id="L316"><td><a href="#L316">316</a></td><td>WORF:  Thank you, sir.</td></tr>

